  <brief_title>Study of Intravenous GMI-1070 in Adults With Sickle Cell Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase 1/Phase 2 Study of the Safety, Pharmacokinetics, and Microvascular Effect of Titrating Doses of Intravenous GMI-1070, a Pan-Selectin Inhibitor, in Adults With Sickle Cell Disease</official_title>
  <sponsors>
