  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This Phase 1/Phase 2 study will evaluate GMI-1070, a pan-selectin inhibitor, in adults with
      stable sickle cell disease. The study will assess safety, pharmacokinetics, and microvascular
      effects of intravenous GMI-1070 in the outpatient setting.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
